reviews.review_text: Far from listening I can't imagine the person who looks at this setlist and says, Yeah!  Far From Me!  Crank it up baby!

Far From Me/Cartwheels I kind of like Far from me - maybe not to close the first or in the 2nd set, but...

Not a bad show - nice estimate/Eyes.  Thought I saw a video of Belushi during US Blues years ago.  But I can't find it anywhere?
